-- Air Mauritius May Appoint Thomas as Chairman, lexpress.mu Says
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-07-26T07:51:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-26/air-mauritius-may-appoint-thomas-as-chairman-lexpress-mu-says.html
Air Mauritius Ltd. (AML)  will probably
name Appalsamy Thomas as chairman at its shareholders’ meeting,
Port Louis-based  lexpress.mu  reported on its website, without
saying where it got the information.  Donald Payen, executive vice president for corporate
communications at the airline, wasn’t immediately available to
comment when contacted by phone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  